    "The proposed new roof and rear dormer window, by reason of their crown roof design and excessive bulk, scale and mass respectively, would appear as incongruous and visually intrusive features in the street scene and rear garden environment, thereby harming the character and appearance of the host property and surrounding area, contrary to Local Plan Policy 7 and the Residential Extensions and Alterations Supplementary Planning Document.",
